<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have a Mithril 2h and am going to buy a TBB since FBSS would be worthless.  My str would then be 151 which isn't bad for a human paladin.  Up until I got my Mith I had a nathsar GS and was saving up for an FBSS.  I think the Mith and the TBB are a great choice and I have hit for 88 without a str buff or TBB.  With Nathsar max was 79 fully buffed ( shaman str buff strength and wolf, had an attack of 993)</font></td></tr></table>
