<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have to thank the person that finally mentioned bards! My bard has 114 str right now (which i think is pretty good for a bard!) and I'm banking on a TBB vs FBSS. For one thing, I have two haste songs right now that stack, and I get an even more powerful haste song in a few more levels. Also, with the 8ac, I can afford to loose my jagged bands and put on my rings that have extra cha (the power behind my songs). I have just gotten back into the swing of soloing (i absolutely could not solo between 18 and 28, but mainly cuz i suck!) and having that +15 str and 8ac is going to be SO much help. It's just the much better choice for a bard. Too bad I can't afford the current price. Guess I gotta get my level 45+ friends to camp one for me... yeah right!</font></td></tr></table>
